** Story **
Once upon a time in a forest there was a monkey on a berry tree on the bank of the river and in that river 
also lived crocodile and his wife...
One day the crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested uder the tree.
The kinf hearted monkey offered him some berries.
The crocodile came back the next day for more berries as he loved them.
As days passed by, the crocodile and the monkey became good friends.
One day the monkey sent some berries to the crocodile's wife.
She ate the berries and loved them but was jealous as she did not ike crocodile spending time with the monkey.
She told her husband, if the fruits are so juicy, how sweet the monkey's heart would be.
She told the crocodile to get the heart of the monkey for her.